1.80(1+i)^{-1}
(1.04)(1+i)^{-1}
22.40 = 1.80(1+i)^{-1}+1.08(1.04)(1+i)^{-2}+...
22.40 = 1.80(1+i)^{-1}\frac{1}{1-(1.04)(1+i)^{-1}}
